quran[8{c,v,t}:
14,11,"un ke Rasolo-n ne un se kaha"" waqai hum kuch nahi hain magar tum hi jaisay ensaan lekin Allah apne bundon mein se jis ko chahta hai nwazta hai aur yeh hamaray ikhtiyar mein nahi hai ke tumhe koi sanad laa den sanad to Allah hi ke azan se askati hai aur Allah hi par ahal imaan ko bharosa karna chahiye"
14,12,"aur hum kyun nah Allah par bharosa karen jabkay hamari zindagi ki raahon mein is ne hamari rahnumai ki hai? jo azeeyaten tum log hamein day rahay ho unn par hum sabr karen ge aur bhrosa karne walon ka bhrosa Allah hi par hona chahiye """
14,13,"aakhir-kaar munkareen ne apne Rasolo-n se keh diya ke"" ya to tumhe hamari millat mein wapas aana hoga warna hum tumhe apne malik se nikaal den ge"" tab unn ke rab ne unn par wahi bhaije ke"" hum inn zaalmon ko hila kaaf kar den ge"
14,14,"aur unn ke baad tumhe zameen mein abad karen ge yeh inaam hai uss ka jo mere huzoor jawab dahi ka khauf rakhta ho aur meri waeed se darta ho """
14,15,onhon ne faisla chaha tha ( to yun unn ka faisla howa ) aur har Jabbar dushman haq ne mun ki khayi
14,16,phir is ke baad agay is ke liye jahannum hai wahan ussay kutch lahoo ka sa pani peenay ko diya jaye ga
14,17,jisay woh zabardasti halaq se utaarnay ki koshish kere ga aur mushkil hi se utaar sakay ga mout har taraf se is par chhai rahay gi magar woh marnay nah paye ga aur agay aik sakht azaab is ki jaan ka laago rahay ga
14,18,jin logon ne apne rab se kufar kya hai un ke aamaal ki misaal uss raakh ki si hai jisay aik tofani din ki aandhi ne ura diya ho woh apne kiye ka kuch bhi phal nah pa saken ge yahi parlay darjay ki gum gushtagihai
